    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, boil a kettle</p><p>Peel and finely slice the <strong>red onion<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong></p><p>Return the pan to a medium heat with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong></p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>sliced red onion</strong> with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and cook for 5 min or until beginning to soften</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
