      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, add the <strong>couscous</strong> and<strong> sultanas</strong> to a heatproof bowl with 200ml<span class=\"text-danger\"> [400ml]</span><strong> boiled water</strong>, cover and set aside</p>",
